All Implemented Interfaces:
MetadataObject
public final class AttributeMap
extends ValueMap

A ValueMap that maps an MdmAttribute for an MdmDimension to an Expression. An application creates an AttributeMap with the findOrCreateAttributeMap method of a DimensionMap. An application that supports multiple languages must provide a separate AttributeMap for each language.
